    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Valdis</strong> 将塔防策略与快节奏第三人称射击以及生存元素完美结合。你将对抗越来越危险的变异丧尸大军——从缓慢的行尸到高速自爆单位，甚至隐形敌人。每个关卡都将考验你的战术思维、反应速度与战场掌控能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">🎭 <strong>故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >空间站 Valdis 发生严重事故，全体船员感染致命丧尸病毒。你是唯一的幸存者。在这场科幻噩梦中，你必须利用自动防御炮塔与强力霰弹枪，在紧张刺激的 <strong>wave defense survival（波次防守生存）</strong> 模式中守护能源核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/b90e260b1514b3eceafdd4650e2c3fec.poster.avif?t=1772059296\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/b90e260b1514b3eceafdd4650e2c3fec.webm?t=1772059296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/b90e260b1514b3eceafdd4650e2c3fec.mp4?t=1772059296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">🎮 <strong>游戏玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用多种炮塔类型：爆能炮、激光炮、迫击炮、自动炮等防御结构。合理组合，打造高效的 <strong>基地防御（Base Defense）</strong> 战略。精准布局、资源管理与对敌人波次的灵活应对是生存的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每座炮塔拥有三种元素之一：火、冰、水。<strong>元素战斗系统（Elemental Combat）</strong> 可对敌人施加减速、燃烧与群体控制效果。通过元素之间的反应触发更强大的连锁效果与毁灭性协同。尝试不同构筑，找到最适合你的防御策略</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/7c4642b31b1c977c4a094a1e279e1cd4.poster.avif?t=1772059296\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/7c4642b31b1c977c4a094a1e279e1cd4.webm?t=1772059296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/7c4642b31b1c977c4a094a1e279e1cd4.mp4?t=1772059296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🧪 试玩版内容</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Valdis 提供初步体验：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– 3 种炮塔类型<br>– 3 种元素<br>– 3 种敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整版将加入更多炮塔、元素、独特敌人、更高难度波次以及更丰富的战略深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们重视你的反馈！欢迎留下评价与建议——也许你的想法会成为正式版本的一部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/e5756ff0973866e56f78871f6daeb50e.poster.avif?t=1772059296\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/e5756ff0973866e56f78871f6daeb50e.webm?t=1772059296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002220/extras/e5756ff0973866e56f78871f6daeb50e.mp4?t=1772059296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⭐ <strong>游戏特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 塔防 + 第三人称射击混合玩法<br>🚀 科幻太空背景<br>🧟 波次丧尸生存挑战<br>🛡️ 战略型基地防御<br>⚡ 元素系统与元素反应<br>🎯 战术炮塔部署<br>💥 快节奏第三人称射击<br>🧠 多样化构筑与策略<br>👾 多种拥有独特能力的敌人<br>🔄 高重玩价值与逐步提升的难度</p>",
